  "id": "cmtrace-web",
  "name": "CMTrace Web",
  "description": "CMTrace Web (CMTrace.dev) is a free, browser-based log viewer for ConfigMgr/SCCM and Intune logs. Reimplementing CMTrace in the browser, it handles 1M+ line logs with color-coded severities, error-code lookups, and side-by-side diffs, all client-side and offline as a PWA. It opens .log, .txt, .gz, and .zip, with Intune/IME presets to jump straight to relevant logs.",
